Dask

```json
{
  "application": "Dask",
  "software": [
    "gcc/7.4.0",
    "cuda/10.1.243",
    "python/3.7.0-anaconda3-5.3.0",
    "nvrapids_0.14_gcc_7.4.0"
  ],
  "resources": [
    "batch node",
    "infiniband network",
    "GPU (gpumps)",
    "512GB memory"
  ],
  "scheduler": {
    "type": "dask-scheduler",
    "port": "randomly selected between 4000-6000",
    "dashboard_address": "hostname:randomly selected between 7000-8999",
    "interface": "ib0",
    "scheduler_file": "my-scheduler.json"
  },
  "workers": {
    "type": "dask-worker",
    "num_workers": "number of nodes allocated to the job minus 1, multiplied by 42",
    "cores_per_worker": 1,
    "memory_per_worker": "512GB divided by the total number of cores",
    "scheduler_file": "my-scheduler.json",
    "interface": "ib0",
    "local_directory": "DASK_DIR"
  }
}
```
